Auto monthly sales during the month of  February reported mixed bag.  Bajaj Auto  Ashok Leyland  M&M reported  good set of monthly sales  volumes while Maruti and Eicher Motor  announced marginally lower than  expected sales volumes.
Besides  two-wheeler players Bajaj Auto  Royal Enfield  TVS Motor and Hero MotoCorp also reported strong double digit sales.

Bajaj Auto rose 0.01%. The company said that its total sales rose 31% to  3.57 lakh units in February 2018 over February 2017. Bajaj Auto's  domestic sales rose 35% to 2.14 lakh units in February 2018 over  February 2017. Exports surged 26% to 1.43 lakh units.
